|  epub       |   fbreader   |
|             |   calibre    |
|  djvu       |   djview4    |
|  mobi       |   fbreader   |
|  fb2        |   fbreader   | 
|  OpenReader |   fbreader   | 
|  rtf        |   fbreader   | 
